c: 9
v: 34
t: "oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Ndithudi ambiri a Atsogoleri a Chiyuda ndi Abusa a Chikhristu amadya chumacha anthumunjirayosalungamandipoamatsekereza kunjira ya Mulungu. Ndi iwo amene amasonkhanitsa golide ndi siliva ndipo sapereka chumacho mu njira ya Mulungu, auzeni za chilango chowawa"